   "source": [
    "# Notes for TensorScatteringClass\n",
    "\n",
    "## Invert system\n",
    "\n",
    "sitevec -> -sitevec\n",
    "\n",
    "normal:\n",
    "\n",
    "r1 = A r0 + V\n",
    "=>  -r1 = -A r0 -V   (1)\n",
    "    \n",
    "inverted\n",
    "-r1 = A* (-r0) + V*  (2)\n",
    "\n",
    "A* = A\n",
    "V* = -V\n",
    "\n",
    "i.e. sg[1] invertsed but not sg[0] or sg[2] - OK (this is what we had before; all good).\n",
    "\n"
   ]
